00:03:14.590 --> 00:03:16.190
Merci pour vos conseils.

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:17.430
Aussi,

00:03:17.750 --> 00:03:19.590
Shizai vient de me le dire

00:03:19.630 --> 00:03:20.750
